<h2 id="插件">插件</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=NoahRichards.GoToDefinition">Go To Definition</a></p>

    <p>Make ctrl+click perform a “Go To Definition” on the identifier under the cursor.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=WholeTomatoSoftware.VisualAssist">Visual Assist</a></p>

    <p>Productivity tool for C/C++ and C# that improves IDE features related to navigation, refactoring, code generation, and coding assistance.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

